      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being lost though. it feels like i've finally reached the actual end. the path doesn't just get harder, it just stops. i'm standing at the very edge of everything and there's nothing beyond it. it's so quiet here. so still. it feels almost... peaceful to just stop trying to find a way through the trees. like there's nothing left to do but just stand here at the edge.",
